<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Task</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .edit-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(40px) scale(0.95);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            }
        }

        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 50px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .edit-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .edit-icon svg {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            stroke: white;
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 2.5;
        }

        .card-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .card-header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .task-meta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 50px;
            background: #fafbfc;
        }

        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .form-field {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .form-field.full-width {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .field-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .required-star {
            color: #e53e3e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .field-input,
        .field-select,
        .field-textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #2d3748;
            background: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: inherit;
            outline: none;
        }

        .field-input::placeholder,
        .field-textarea::placeholder {
            color: #a0aec0;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .field-input:focus,
        .field-select:focus,
        .field-textarea:focus {
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            background: #fafbff;
        }

        .field-input:hover:not(:focus),
        .field-select:hover:not(:focus),
        .field-textarea:hover:not(:focus) {
            border-color: #cbd5e0;
            background: #f7fafc;
        }

        .field-input:disabled,
        .field-select:disabled,
        .field-textarea:disabled {
            background: #f7fafc;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .field-select {
            appearance: none;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='12' height='8' viewBox='0 0 12 8' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M1 1.5L6 6.5L11 1.5' stroke='%23667eea' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: right 18px center;
            padding-right: 45px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .field-textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .info-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: start;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .info-banner svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            stroke: #667eea;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .info-content h3 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4c51bf;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .info-content p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #5a67d8;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 35px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .btn svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }

        .btn-save {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-save:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-save:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-cancel {
            background: #f7fafc;
            color: #4a5568;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover {
            background: #edf2f7;
            border-color: #cbd5e0;
        }

        .btn-delete {
            background: #fff5f5;
            color: #e53e3e;
            border: 2px solid #feb2b2;
        }

        .btn-delete:hover {
            background: #fed7d7;
            border-color: #fc8181;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-calendar-picker-indicator {
            cursor: pointer;
            opacity: 0.6;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            padding: 2px;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-calendar-picker-indicator:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit {
            padding: 0;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-fields-wrapper {
            padding: 0;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-text {
            color: #a0aec0;
            padding: 0 2px;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-month-field,
        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-day-field,
        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-year-field {
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-month-field:focus,
        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-day-field:focus,
        input[type="date"]::-webkit-datetime-edit-year-field:focus {
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            color: #667eea;
            outline: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }

            .card-header {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }

            .card-header h1 {
                font-size: 26px;
            }

            .card-body {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }

            .form-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 25px;
            }

            .button-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="edit-card">
            
            <div class="card-header">
                <div class="header-content">
                    <div class="edit-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"></path>
                            <path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h1>Edit Task</h1>
                    <p>Update and manage your task information</p>
                    <div class="task-meta">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                            <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line>
                        </svg>
                        Task ID: T-12345
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body">

                <div class="info-banner">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                        <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                        <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <h3>You're Editing an Existing Task</h3>
                        <p>Make your changes below and click "Save Changes" to update this task in your system.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <form method="POST" action="/edittask">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Id" value="12345">

                    <div class="form-grid">

                        <div class="form-field full-width">
                            <label class="field-label">
                                Task Name
                                <span class="required-star">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <input type="text" name="Name" class="field-input" required placeholder="Enter task name..." value="Complete project documentation">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">
                                Start Date
                                <span class="required-star">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <input type="date" name="AssignDate" class="field-input" required value="2025-01-01">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">
                                Due Date
                                <span class="required-star">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <input type="date" name="DueDate" class="field-input" required value="2025-01-15">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">
                                Priority Level
                                <span class="required-star">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <select name="priority" class="field-select" required>
                                <option value="" disabled>Select priority</option>
                                <option value="low">üü¢ Low Priority</option>
                                <option value="medium" selected>üü° Medium Priority</option>
                                <option value="high">üî¥ High Priority</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">
                                Current Status
                                <span class="required-star">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <select name="status" class="field-select" required>
                                <option value="" disabled>Select status</option>
                                <option value="pending">‚è≥ Pending</option>
                                <option value="in-progress">üîÑ In Progress</option>
                                <option value="completed">‚úÖ Completed</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">Category</label>
                            <select name="category" class="field-select">
                                <option value="" disabled>Choose category</option>
                                <option value="work" selected>üíº Work</option>
                                <option value="personal">üè† Personal</option>
                                <option value="shopping">üõí Shopping</option>
                                <option value="health">üí™ Health & Fitness</option>
                                <option value="study">üìö Study</option>
                                <option value="other">üìå Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field">
                            <label class="field-label">Assigned To</label>
                            <input type="text" name="assignedTo" class="field-input" placeholder="Enter name..." value="John Doe">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field full-width">
                            <label class="field-label">Tags</label>
                            <input type="text" name="tags" class="field-input" placeholder="e.g., urgent, client-work, design" value="urgent, documentation">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field full-width">
                            <label class="field-label">Description</label>
                            <textarea name="description" class="field-textarea" placeholder="Add detailed notes about this task...">Need to complete the full project documentation including API docs and user guides.</textarea>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="button-container">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-save">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                <path d="M19 21H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11l5 5v11a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                                <polyline points="17 21 17 13 7 13 7 21"></polyline>
                                <polyline points="7 3 7 8 15 8"></polyline>
                            </svg>
                            Save Changes
                        </button>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-cancel">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                            </svg>
                            Cancel
                        </a>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-delete" onclick="if(confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this task?')) alert('Task deleted!')">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                <polyline points="3 6 5 6 21 6"></polyline>
                                <path d="M19 6v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V6m3 0V4a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2"></path>
                            </svg>
                            Delete
                        </button>
                    </div>

                </form>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>